names leading the declines as investors punished Cisco Systems despite a profit
report that topped Wall Street's expectations. Cisco shares were down 3 3/8 at
59 3/8. Just before 11 a.m. EDT, the Dow industrials were down 98.18 at
10,438.57. On the NYSE, decliners led advancers 1,587-770. The Nasdaq was down
134.44 at 3,450.57.
