<HEADLINE> London Share Prices Fall  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   LONDON (AP) -- Share prices were lower on the London Stock
Exchange Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
   The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-Share Index of blue chip
stocks closed down 23.2 points, or 0.4 percent, at 6,100.6.
</P>
<P>
   Volume was 1.7 billion shares, an increase from 1.39 billion on
Tuesday.
</P>
</TEXT>
