<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Big Movers in the Stock Market  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks that moved substantially or traded
heavily Wednesday on the New York Stock Exchange and Nasdaq Stock
Market.
</P>
<P>
NYSE
</P>
<P>
Champion International, up 6 1/16 at 72]
</P>
<P>
   Both International Paper and Finnish company UPM-Kymmene
sweetened their bids for Champion. The new IP bid values Champion
